overview:
J1 employment solutions for staff-conscious firms in need of extra workers in summer.

Exchange students represent countries such as Russia, China, Ukraine, Mongolia, Belarus, Kazakhstan, Turkey etc. The age of our students varies from 18 to 24 years, but most are 19 to 21 years of age. J1 Visa students can work from May/June to September/October.

If you wish to obtain examples of profiles with photos of J1 visa students, please contact Jobofer.org.

It is all COMPLETELY FREE to you as the employer.

Register here http://www.jobofer.org/employer/register/crunchbase/
